---
title: Teriyaki Mushroom Noodle Stir-Fry with Crushed Peanuts
description: Load your bowl with tender ramen noodles plus a medley of colourful veggies. With our easy teriyaki sauce to bring the whole meal together, this feast will have you throwing away the takeaway menu!
